gov.ca.dsm2.input.model.diff
Class DSM2ModelDiff

java.lang.Object
  gov.ca.dsm2.input.model.diff.DSM2ModelDiff

public class DSM2ModelDiff
extends java.lang.Object

This object contains the result of diffing two DSM2Models. In other words model2-model1 is something like this model If an element in model2 is identical in model 1 then it is not present in the diff If an element in model2 is not identical in model 1, the it is present here as the original element in model 1 and the new element in model 2 If an element in model 2 is not present in model 1, it is considered a pure add and the element in model 1 is null If an element in model 1 is not present in model 2, it is considered a pure delete and the element in model 2 is null
